text:
Croton Aqueduct (old), south from but not including West Burnside Ave. The old aqueduct runs between Harrison (left) and University Aves. and shows the rears of buildings which face on the two thoroughfares. The vantage-point is the 5-story building No. 1925-1935 Harrison Ave., adjoining the S.W. corner of West Burnside Ave.

August 5, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Bronx: West Burnside Avenue - betw. Harrison Avenue - University Avenue.
